I '''Julius Richard Petri''' (Mayo 31, 1852 &ndash; Diciembre 20, 1921) metung yang bakteriologung [[Alemania|Aleman]] a tuturing da reng keraklan a menimbentu king [[Petri dish]] kabang magobra antimong assistant nang [[Robert Koch]].

Minuna yang megaral medisina i Petri king Kaiser-Wilhelm-Academy for Military Physicians (1871–1875) at tinanggap yang titulu king medisina anyang (''medical degree'') anyang 1876. Sindu na ing kayang pamagaral king [[Charité|Charité Hospital]] king [[Berlin]] at atyu king aktibung serbisyu antimong doktor a militar anggang 1882, at kaybat, sindu na iti antimong reserbista. 

Manibat 1877 anggang 1879, mituldu ya king Imperial Health Office ({{lang-de|Kaiserliches Gesundheitsamt}}) king [[Berlin]], nung nu ne meging assistant Robert Koch.  King usuk o abisu nang Angelina Hesse, ing asawa ning aliwang assistant a mibait New York, i [[Walter Hesse|Walther Hesse]], inumpisan ning laboratoryung Koch ing pamagpatubung bacteria kareng [[agar]] plate. Kaybat, inimbentu neng Petri ing ''standard culture dish'', o Petri plate, at lalu ne pang inalkus (''further developed'') ing kaparalanan ning pamagpatubu king agar culture ba lang gawang puru at parakalan deng kolonyang bacteria a ibat kareng magdili-diling selula (''single cells''). Uli na ning panyulung a iti, meging posibling kilalanan la king masusing peralan deng bacteriang panibatan da reng sakit.

